value.title: Biden's pick of Denis McDonough for VA sparks pushback from veterans
value.excerpt: The aftermath of President-elect Joe Biden’s pick for secretary of Veteran Affairs has been met with responses of “surprise” after long-time Obama aide Denis McDonough was selected to be only the second non-veteran to take up the seat Thursday.

value.title: Biden facing pressure to pick Congresswoman Deb Haaland as Interior Secretary

value.title: President Trump secures deal between Israel and Morocco in a Hanukkah miracle

value.title: Pence says Trump ‘deserves his day’ in Supreme Court
